data.description: LOCATION...LOCATION..VIEWS ATOP OF THIS 5TH FLOOR UNIT,WEST FACING WATER AND EAST TO THE MOUNTAINS! Welcome to this stunning 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom modern condo located in the heart of National City. Boasting an open floor plan,ample natural light. The bedroom features generous closet space and a private EAST FACING deck with amazing mountain views.Kitchen is equipped with granite countertops & plenty of storage space. Enjoy the convenience of living just minutes from the I-5 freeway and Naval Base San Diego and the newly completed 8th AVE Mercado for coffee and great eats !
